01:02:27.610 --> 01:02:37.670 align:middle line:90%


01:02:37.670 --> 01:02:43.750 align:middle line:84%
Step one, so if we start with
a single unipotent orbit,

01:02:43.750 --> 01:02:47.950 align:middle line:84%
