point like this.

01:02:47.950 --> 01:02:52.710 align:middle line:84%
So that's u 0, 1
of some point x.

01:02:52.710 --> 01:02:54.500 align:middle line:90%
What happens when we apply Lar?

01:02:54.500 --> 01:03:00.270 align:middle line:90%


01:03:00.270 --> 01:03:05.400 align:middle line:84%
Well, this thing is going
to get tall and skinny.

01:03:05.400 --> 01:03:09.420 align:middle line:90%


01:03:09.420 --> 01:03:11.660 align:middle line:84%
And the direction
that got stretched

01:03:11.660 --> 01:03:13.660 align:middle line:90%
