01:03:13.660 --> 01:03:16.900 align:middle line:84%
So now we're going
to have a long orbit.

01:03:16.900 --> 01:03:21.460 align:middle line:84%
And the height of this
thing is e to the 2r.

01:03:21.460 --> 01:03:24.620 align:middle line:90%
Then we're getting a quotient.

01:03:24.620 --> 01:03:26.180 align:middle line:84%
So when we quotient,
